title: Yak and Yetti - Arvada
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Nepalese, Tibetan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Himalayan cuisine (Nepal and Indian) and handcrafted beer. Buffet at lunchtime, a la carte menu dinner. While the menu is primarily meat, the website shows a vegetarian section with around 15 main dishes, and on premises you will also find a vegan menu.
